quran[171]{c,v,t}:
  27,56,"Jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano si wanaa ko …ìe wi'i : \"Yaltinee yim…ìe Luutu …ìen ka ho…óo (wura) moo…óon ; kam…ìe ko …ìe yim…ìe la…ì…ìintintoo…ìe"
  27,57,"Men da…óndi mo kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen, si wanaa debbo makko on; [on …óon] Men hoddiranii mo ko o jeyaa…óo e halketaa…ìe …ìen"
  27,58,"Men to…ìini e dow ma…ì…ìe to…ìo, bonii to…ìo jertinaa…ìe …ìen"
  27,59,"Maaku: Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, kisiyee wonii e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen …ìe O su…ìii. Enee, ko Alla …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, kaa ko …óin …ói…ìe sirkanta"
  27,60,"Kaa ko hommbo tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin O jippinani on immorde ka kammu ndiyam? Men fu…óiniri …óam gese joomiraaje ≈ãari. Wonantaa on nde fu…óinon le…ó…óe majje. Enee, hara rewetee…óo no woodi wonndude e Alla? Ko woni, kam…ìe ko …ìe yim…ìe oo√±otoo…ìe"
  27,61,"Kaa ko hommbo wa…ói leydi ndin √±ii…ìundi, O wa…ói hakkunde mayri callu…ói O wa…óani ndi pelle O wa…ói hakkunde maaje …óen …ói…ói heedo? Enee, hara na woodi rewetee…óo [goo] wonndude e Alla? ko woni, …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude …ìen e ma…ì…ìe …ìe anndaa"
  27,62,Kaa ko hommbo jaabato …ìittii…óo on si o noddi Mo o hunca bone …óen O wa…óa on lontii…ìe ka leydi? Na woodi Korewetee…óo goo wonndude e Alla? Fan…óii ko waajito…óon
  27,63,"Kaa ko hommbo fewnata on ka ni…ìe njoorndi e ka maayo, e ko hommbo accitata keni …óin wewliniray…ói fii Yurmeende Makko nden? Enee, ko rewetee…óo goo wonndude e Alla? Alla Toowii gaayi ko …ìe sirkata kon. @Corrected"
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo woni fu…ó…óu…óo tagu ngun refti O rutta ngu, e ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Enee, ko rewetee…óo goo wonndude e Alla? Maaku: \"Addee daliili moo…óon on si tawii ko on goongu…ìe"
  27,65,"Maaku: \"Anndaa ko wirnii kon …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wanaa Alla. ∆Åe so'ataa kadi ko honnde tuma …ìe immintinoytee"
  27,66,"Ko woni, ganndal ma…ì…ìe ngal hattii fii Laakara on, ko woni, kam…ìe hi…ìe e sikke fii [Laakara], ko woni, kam…ìe ko …ìe wumu…ìe fii …óum"
  27,67,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe wi'i: \" Enee, hay si men laatike mbullaari e baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen kadi, e hara menen ko men yaltinoytee…ìe"
  27,68,"Gom…óii men fodanooma …óum menen e baabiraa…ìe amen ko adii, …óum wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinoo…ìe"
  27,69,"Maaku : \"Yehee ka leydi ndaaron ko honno battane bon…ìe …ìen laatornoo"
  27,70,"Wata a suno fii ma…ì…ìe, wata a laato e …ìitteende immorde e ko …ìe fewjata kon"
  27,71,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goongu…ìe"
  27,72,"Maaku: \"No tijjaa nde tawata …ìadanike on yoga e kon ko …óa…ì…ìu…óon yaccinaneede"
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa ko O Jom ∆Åural e dow yim…ìe …ìen, kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude …ìen e ma…ì…ìe …ìe jarnataa [Alla]"
  27,74,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa hiMo Anndi ko …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen soomi e ko …óe fe√±√±inta kon"
  27,75,"Alaa e wirniikun ka kammu e ka leydi si wanaa [fii makkun] no e nder Deftere …ìanngunde"
  27,76,"Pellet ndee Alqur'aanaare, hinde filloo e dow …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen fii huunde nde …ìe …ìuri luutondirde nden e fii muu…óum"
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonannde gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa O √±aawiray hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √ëaawoore Makko ngal, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Anndu…óo"
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an hi…óa e hoore Goonga …ìannguka kan"
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa may…ìe …ìen, a nanintaa faa…óu…ìe …ìen noddaandu ndun si …ìe …óuurnike …ìe huccitii"
  27,81,An a wonaali fewnoowo bum…ìe …ìen e gaayi majjere ma…ì…ìe nden. A nanintaa si wanaa …ìen gom…óin…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ìe ko …ìe jebbilii…ìe
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow ma…ì…ìe, Men yaltinana …ìe daabewa immorde ka leydi himba haalana …ìe wonnde yim…ìe …ìen laatike …ìe yananaaka Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  27,83,E √±alnde Men moo…ìoyta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaa…ìe e …ìen fennoo…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ìe hi…ìe soggee
  27,84,"Haa si …ìe arii, O Daala: \"Eyoo, on fenniino Aayeeje Am …óen, hara on hu…ìindoraali …ói ganndal. Kaa ko hon…óum won…óon e gollude"
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e ma…ì…ìe sabu ko …ìe too√±i kon, kam…ìe …ìe wowlataa"
  27,86,"Enee, hara …ìe yi'aali, Menen Men wa…óii jemma on fii yo …ìe dee∆¥u e maako, e √±alorma on yi'ir…óo? Pellet, wonii e …óum Aayeeje wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe …ìen"
  27,87,"E √ëalnde wuttoytee ka alaadu, …óen∆¥oo …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli e …ìen wonu…ìe ka leydi, si wanaa …ìen …ìe Alla muuyi, gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe aray e Makko hara ko …ìe hoykinii…ìe"
  27,88,"Hi…óa tina pelle …óen, sikka ko …óe fenndii…óe, hara le kannje hi…óe wuloo wulagol duule …óen, …óum ko kuugal Alla, On ≈ãar…óin…óo kala huunde, pellet, Kanko ko O Humpitii…óo ko golloton kon"
  27,89,"Mo ardii e mo∆¥∆¥ere nden haray no woodani mo ko …ìuri nde mo∆¥∆¥ude, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe hoolii…ìe immorde e …óen∆¥ere nden √ëalnde"
  27,90,"Mo ardii kadi e bone …óen, geece ma…ì…ìe …óen hippete ka Yiite. Yalli on yo…ìete si wanaa kon ko laatino…óon hi…óon golla"
  27,91,"Anndu ko mi yamiraa ko yo mi Rewu Jooma ndii leydi ndi Alla harmini …óum, no woodani Mo kala huunde. Mi yamiraama kadi yo mi laato jeyaa…óo e jebbilii…ìe …ìen"
  27,92,"E yo mi janngu Alqur'aanaare nden, mo feewii haray ko hoore-makko o feewani, mo majjii kadi haray maaku: \"Min dey, ko mi jeyaa…óo e jertinoo…ìe …ìen"
  27,93,"Maaku kadi: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla, aray O holla on Aayeeje Makko …óen anndon …óe\". Joomi maa…óa wonaali welsindii…óo gaay e kon ko golloton"
  28,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim"
  28,2,∆äee ko Aayeeje Deftere …ìanngunde nden
  28,3,"Me…óen janngira e maa…óa hoore goonga, kumpital Muusaa e Fir'awna, wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,4,"Pellet, Fir'awna townitino ka leydi; o wa…ói yim…ìe mayri ndin pecce-pecce: himo lo'ina fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe, o hirsa …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe wor…ìe …ìen o acca rew…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen. Pellet, ko e bonnoo…ìe …ìen o jeyanoo"
  28,5,"Me…óen faandinoo mo∆¥∆¥agol e lo'inanoo…ìe …ìen ka leydi; Men wa…óa …ìe koohoo…ìe, Men wa…óa …ìe kadi ronoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,6,"Men hu…ìindina …ìe e leydi ndin, Men holla Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli ma…ì…ìe …óin, kon ko …ìe hulaynoo"
  28,7,"Men wahayini e yumma Muusaa, wonnde: \"Muynin mo\". Si a hulanoyii mo, ko yo a bugoyo mo ka maayo. Wata a hulu, wata a suno; pellet, Men ruttay mo ka maa…óa, Men wa…óoya mo gooto e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  28,8,"Yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen hocci mo, fii yo laatano …ìe ga√±o e suno. Pellet, Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìe laatino woopu…ìe"
  28,9,"Debbo Fir'awna on wi'i: \"(Kun entum ko) …ìuu…ìeendi gite am e an kadi! Wata on waru mo, hino gasa ka o nafata en, maa jogitoren mo …ìi…ó…óo\". Hari …ìe so'aani"
  28,10,"∆Åernde yumma Muusaa nden wonti yeewunde. Haa o e…ì…ìi fe√±√±inde fii makko, si wanaano Men tabintinnde …ìernde makko nden, fii yo o laato e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  28,11,"[Yumma Muusaa] wi'ani banndiraawo makko on: \"Jokkitu mo\"; o haynii mo ka deestii, hari …ìe so'aa-anndude"
  28,12,"Men harminani mo ko adii, (en…ói) muynir…ói …óin, (banndiraawo makko on) wi'i: \"On accay mi tinndinay on fii yim…ìe suudu, …ìe ne'ana on mo, hara kadi ko laa…ìanay …ìe mo"
  28,13,"Men rutti mo ka yumma makko, fii yo …ìernde makko …ìuu…ìu, hara o sunaaki, e fii yo o anndu pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe anndaa"
  28,14,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, o fotondi- ri, Men okki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano non Men yo…ìirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,15,"O naatiri e saare nden, fewndo welsindaare yim…ìe mayre; o tawi wor…ìe …ói…óo no ha…ìa ton: go…ó…óo on ko jeyaa…óo e le√±ol makko, oya on ko jeyaa…óo e ay…ìe makko …ìen. Jeyaa…óo e le√±ol makko ngol …óa…ì…ìiri faabo e hoore jeyaa…óo e ga√±o makko on. Muusaa uttii mo, nde gayni fii makko. [Muusaa] maaki: \"∆äum …óoo, ko jeyaa…óum e kuu…óe seytaane. Pellet, ko o ga√±o, majjinoowo …ìanngu…óo"
  28,16,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi too√±ii hoore-am; haforanam.\" O haforani mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  28,17,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, sabu ko neemin…óaa kon e am, mi wontataa ballo bom…ìe …ìen"
  28,18,"O wonti hul…óo ka saare, himo habbii [nanngeede]. Tawi faabinornoo…óo mo on hanki, hino faabinora mo [hannde kadi]. Muusaa maakani mo: \"Pellet, ko a bew…óo …ìanngu…óo"
  28,19,"Nde Muusaa faandinoo nanngugol taw…óo on ko ga√±o ma…ì…ìe kam…ìe …ói…óo, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, a faala warugol lam, wano ittirno…óaa wonkii non hanki? A faandaaki, si wanaa wonugol dunndarankeejo ka leydi, a faandaaki jeyeede e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ìuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, himo yaccoo, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, mbatu ngun no fewjana fii warugol maa. Yaltu (e leydi ndin). Ko mi jeyaa…óo e laa…ìanoo…ìe ma"
  28,21,"O yalti ton, ko o hulu…óo, himo tijjii [nanngeede]. O maaki: \"Joomi am, dan…óndam e yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,22,"Nde o fewtunoo hella Madyana, o maaki: \"Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol focciingol ngol"
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka …ìunndu Madyana, o tawi …óon dental yim…ìe, hi…ìe yarna [daabeeji ma…ì…ìe], o tawi gaanin ma…ì…ìe, rew…ìe …ói…óo, no sogga [dammi ma…ì…ìe], o maaki: \"Ko hon…óum habbi-…óon?\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Men yarnataa haa aynoo…ìe …ìen deestoo, baaba amen, ko maw…óo nayeejo"
  28,24,"O yarnani …ìe [dammi …óin], refti o huccitiri ka …óowdi, o maaki: \"Joomi am, min ko jippin…óaa e am woo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, ko mi hatonji…óo"
  28,25,"Gooto e [jiw…ìe] …ìen ari e makko, himo yahra hersa, o wi'i: \"Baaba am no nodde, fii yo o yo…ìe njo…ìdi kon ko yarnan-…óaa men\". Tuma o hewtunoo ka [maw…óo] on, o sifanii mo fii [makko], o maaki: \"Wata a hulu, a da…óii yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,26,"Gooto e [jiw…ìe] …ìen wi'i: \"∆≥ettu mo golle, yo baaba. Pellet, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e mo ∆¥ettataa golle, ko doolnu…óo hoolnii…óo"
  28,27,"[Maw…óo] on maaki: \"Mi…óo yi…ói resingol ma gooto e jiw…ìe am …ìen …óoo …ói…óo, e hoore yo a golla-nam duu…ìi jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa; mi faalaaka sa…ótinannde ma. A taway lam, si Alla ja…ìii, ko e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen mi jeyaa"
  28,28,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"∆äum wonii hakkunde am e mon. Happu woo e majji …ói…ói, …ói mi hunni, haray …ìi…óteede alanaa e lam. En wa…óii Alla fawtii…óo e ko wowlu…óen kon"
  28,29,"Nde Muusaa timminnoo happu ngun, o yahdi e …ìeydnuure makko, o haynii yiite ka senngo (fello) Tuuri, o maaki …ìeunguure makko nden: \"Wonee …óoo, min mi haynike yiite. Belajo'o mi addana on e magge kumpital maa te'annde(docotal) yiite ngen, belajo'o iwloron"
  28,30,"Nde o hewtunoo nge, o noddiraa ka fonngo √±aamo aynde, ka tummbere barkinaande, ka (takko) lekki, wonnde: \"Ko an yo Muusaa! Ko Min woni Alla, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  28,31,"Kadi: \"Bugo tuggordu maa ndun\"; nde o tinunoo hindu dillira wa mboddi,o huccitiri dogudu, o ye∆¥∆¥itaaki. [O noddaa]: \"Ko an yo Muusaa! Artu, wata a hulu; ko a jeyaa…óo e hoolii…ìe …ìen"
  28,32,"Naadu juungo maa ngon ka jayba maa, ngo yaltay ranewo, ko aldaa e √±awu. Bakaa e maa…óa, juu…óe maa …óen, fii kulol ngol. ∆äin ko hujjaaji …ói…ói, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e Fir'awna e dental mun, pellet, …ìen laatike yim…ìe faasiqii…ìe"
  28,33,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi ittiino wonkii e ma…ì…ìe, mi…óo huli nde …ìe warata lam"
  28,34,"Ko musi…ó…óo am on Haaruuna, …ìuri lam laa…ìude …óemngal. Immindin-mo e am, ko wallitoo lam, goonginan-mi; mi…óo huli nde …ìe fennata lam"
  28,35,"[Alla] daali: \"Men semmbiniray tere maa …óen, musi…ó…óo maa on, Men wa…óana on hujja (e cemmbe); …ìe hewtirtaa on …ói…óo, sabu Aayeeje Amen …óe [Men nuli e] mo'on, e …ìen jokku…ìe on foolu…ìe"
  28,36,"Nde Muusaa ardunoo e ma…ì…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen …ìanngu…óe, …ìe wi'i: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu fefindaangu. Men naniraali …óum baabiraa…ìe amen adinoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,37,"Muusaa maaki: \"Ko Joomi am …ìuri anndude on ardu…óo e peewal, immorde ka Makko, e on mo battane mo∆¥∆¥e woodani ka laakara. Pellet, O malnataa too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,38,"Fir'awna wi'i: \"Ko onon dental, mi anndanaa on rewetee…óo, si wanaa min. Ko an yo Haamaana, hu…ì…ìinanam [yiite] e loopal ngal, mahiranaa lam hu…ìeere toowunde, no gasa ka mi ∆¥ellitoo e Rewetee…óo Muusaa On; tawde mi…óo sikki mo e fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,39,"O townitii ka leydi, kanko e koneeli makko …óin, ko aldaa e goonga. ∆Åe sikki wonde …ìe ruttitetaako ka Amen"
  28,40,"Men nanngi mo, kanko e koneeli makko …óin, Men bugii …ìe ka maayo. Tasko, ko honno battane too√±u…ìe …ìen wa'unoo"
  28,41,"Men wa…ói …ìe ardii…ìe, noddoo …ìe e Yiite. √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe walletaake"
  28,42,"Men jokkintiniri …ìe ka aduna …óoo, kuddi. √ëalnde Darngal, ko …ìe jeyaa…ìe e wo…ó…óintinoytee…ìe [e yurmeende Alla]"
  28,43,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, …ìaawo nde Men halkunoo gire arane …óen, ko nde ndayginorde yim…ìe …ìen, e peewal e yurmeende. Belajo'o, …ìe waajitoray"
  28,44,"A tawanooka ka senngo hiirnaange, fewndo Men wahyinnoo e Muusaa yamiroore nden, a jeyanooka kadi e seedii…ìe …ìen"
  28,45,"Kono Menen woni tagu…ìe gire, duu…ìi ma…ì…ìe juuti. A ho…óaano kadi e yim…ìe Madyana …ìen, hi…óa janngana …ìe Aayeeje Amen; ko Menen woni nul…ìe"
  28,46,"A tawanooka ka senngo Fello Tuuri, fewndo Men noddunoo; ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa [woni ko Men nulir-maa], fii no jertiniraa yim…ìe, …ìe reentinoowo araali e ma…ì…ìe, ado maa…óa, belajo'o, …ìe waajitoto"
  28,47,"Si wanaano fii yo lepte yanir e ma…ì…ìe, sabu ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe ardini, …ìe wi'ayno: \"Joomi amen, ko ha…óno imminaa Nulaa…óo e amen? Men jokka nun Aayeeje Maa …óen, men jeyee e gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  28,48,"Nde o addirannoo…ìe goonga kan, immorde ka Amen, …ìe wi'i: \"Ko ha…óno o okkee yeru ko Muusaa okkanoo kon?\" Kere …ìe yeddaano ko Muusaa okkanoo kon ko adii? ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko mbileeji …ói…ói, …ói no wallindira!\" ∆Åe wi'i kadi: \"Ko men yeddu…ìe fow e mun"
  28,49,"Maaku: \"Addee Deftere immorde ka Alla, hara hinde …ìuri …óee …ói…ói feewude, mi jokkaynde, si on laatike goongun…ìe"
  28,50,"Si …ìe jaabaaki ma, anndu ko mbelee…óe ma…ì…ìe …ìe jokkata. Ko hommbo …ìuri majjude …ìuri on jokkir…óo mbelee…óe mun, ko aldaa e peewal immorde ka Alla? Pellet, Alla fewnataa yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,51,"Gom…óii Men hewtinii …ìe Konngol ngol, belajo'o, …ìe waajitora"
  28,52,"∆Åen …ìe Men rokki Deftere [Tawreeta] nden, ko adii [Alqur'aana] ndee, ko …ìe gom…óim…ìe nde"
  28,53,"Si nde janngaama e dow ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii nde. Ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi amen. Pellet men woniino jebbilii…ìe, ado mayre"
  28,54,"∆Åen …óon, …ìe jonniroyte njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, laabi …ói…ói, sabu ko …ìe mu√±inoo kon, hi…ìe du√±iraynoo mo∆¥∆¥ere nden, bone on, e huunde nde Men arsiki …ìe nden, hi…ìe nafqa"
  28,55,"Si …ìe nanii meerente, …ìe …óuurnoo e …óum, …ìe wi'a: \"Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Kisal wonii e mo'on. Men …óa…ì…ìataa wonndugol e majju…ìe …ìen"
  28,56,"Pellet, an (Nulaa…óo), a fewnataa mo yi…óu…óaa; kono Alla no fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko …ìuri anndude feewu…ìe …ìen"
  28,57,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Si men jokkidii peewal ngal e maa, men biftete ka leydi amen\". E Men ho…óiniraali …ìe e nokku horminaa…óo, hoolnii…óo, mo dim…óe noone kaka addetee e mun, arsike immorde ka Amen? Si ko woni, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  28,58,"∆äuu…óii ko Men hakli, e yim…ìe ca'e, bewrunoo…ìe nguuree mun, e hino non galleeji ma…ì…ìe …óin, ho…óiraaka …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa see…óa. Men laatii wonnde ronoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,59,"Joomi maa siforaali wonde halkoowo yim…ìe ca'e, haa O immina e lenyol ma…ì…ìe…óen, Nulaa…óo, ko janngana …ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen. Men siforaali kadi halkugol yim…ìe ca'e, si wanaa hara yim…ìe majje ko too√±u…ìe"
  28,60,"Kala ko okka…óon e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna e cu…óaari mun; ko ko woni ka Alla kon, …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, woni kadi ko luttata. E on haqqiltaa"
  28,61,"E ko on mo Men fodi fodaari mo∆¥∆¥uri, ndi o hawrata e mu'un, wa'ata wa on mo Men dakmitiri dakamme nguurndam aduna, refti hara kanko on, √ëalnde Darngal, ko e tawnetee…ìe (ka Yiite) …ìen o jeyaa"
  28,62,"√ëalnde O noddoyta …ìe, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kafidaa…ói am, …óin …ói aa∆¥orayno…óon woni"
  28,63,"∆Åen …ìe Konngol jojji e mu'un wi'a: \"Joomi amen, ko …ìee woni ko men bewinnoo. Men bewinirno …ìe, wano men bewirnoo. Men da…óndinike e Maa…óa. Wanaa menen …ìe rewaynoo"
  28,64,"[∆Åe] wi'anee: \"Noddee non kafidaa…ói mon …óin\". ∆Åe nodda …ói, kono …ói jaabotaako …ìe. ∆Åe yi'a lepte …óen, (…ìe yeloo) sinno hara …ìe feewuno"
  28,65,"√ëalnde O noddoyta …ìe, o wi'a: \"Ko hon…óum jaabino…óon Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  28,66,"Lamitor…ói …óin wumi…óana …ìe nden √±alnde, …ìe lamndondirtaa"
  28,67,"Si ko tuubu…óo, o gom…óini, o golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói, hino hasii ka o jeyee e malaa…ìe …ìen"
  28,68,"Joomi maa no taga ko O muuyi, O su…ìoo; su…ìagol alanaa …ìe. Senaade woodanii Alla! O toowii e kon ko …ìe sirkata"
  28,69,"Joomi maa no anndi ko …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen suu…óata, e kon ko …ìe fe√±√±inta"
  28,70,"Ko Kanko Alla woni, Mo rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko Kanko yettoore woodani aduna e laakara. Hino woodani Mo √±aawoore nden. Ko ka Makko ruttete…óon"
  28,71,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla wa…óiranii on jemma on, duumii…óo haa √ëalnde Darngal, ko rewetee…óo hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on ndayngu? E on nanataa"
  28,72,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla wa…óiranii on √±alorma on, duumii…óo haa √ëalnde Darngal, ko rewetee…óo hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on jemma, mo dee∆¥oton e mun? E on yi'ataa"
  28,73,"Hino jeyaa e yurmeende Makko, O wa…óiranii on jemma e √±alorma; fii no dee∆¥iron e (jemma) on, e no …óa…ì…ìiron ( e √±alorma on), …ìural Makko, e no belajo'o yettiron [Mo]"
  28,74,"√ëalnde O noddoyta …ìe, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kadidaa…ói(renndidii…ói) am, …óin …óin aa∆¥orayno…óon woni"
  28,75,"Men …óoofi e kala mofte, seedotoo…óo, Men wi'a: \"Addee hujjaajji mon …óin\". ∆Åe anndi wonnde goonga kan, ko Alla woodani; ko …ìe fefindotonoo kon majjitora …ìe"
  28,76,"Pellet,Qaaruuna ko e yim…ìe Muusaa …ìen jeyanoo,kono o bewi e ma…ì…ìe.Men okki mo ngaluuji taway-…ói soktir…óe mun,no teddana jamaa doolnu…óo.Nde yim…ìe makko …ìen,wi'anno mo:Wata a weltor townitaare.Pellet Alla yi…óaa weltortoo…ìe toownitaare"
  28,77,"∆äa…ì…ìir ko Alla okku-maa kon, galle laakare …óen. Wata a yejjitu ge…ìal maa ngal aduna. Mo∆¥∆¥ir no Alla mo∆¥∆¥orii non e maa…óa. Wata a …óa…ì…ìu bonnugol ka leydi. Anndu pellet, Alla yi…óaa bonnoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,78,"O wi'i: \"Ko mi okkiraa …óum, ko e hoore ganndal ngal mi jogii\". E o anndaa wonnde gom…óii Alla halkiino gire, adii…ìe mo, …ìur…ìe doole, …ìuri mo …óuu…óude jawle? ∆Åe lamndoytaake fii junuubi ma…ì…ìe, kam…ìe bom…ìe …ìen"
  28,79,"O yaltitiri e yim…ìe makko …ìen, cu…óaari makko ndin. Yi…óu…ìe nguurndam aduna …ìen wi'i: \"Hara nun men he…ìayno sugu koo ko Qaaruuna okkaa. Kanko on, pellet, ko o jom-ge…ìal mawnungal"
  28,80,"Okkaa…ìe ganndal …ìen kan wi'i: \"Ee bone mon! Ko mbarjaari Alla ndin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on gom…óin…óo o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i\". Kono hawrataa e …óum, si wanaa mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen"
  28,81,"Men mutindini mo e galle makko …óen, ka leydi. Fedde woo alanaa mo, ko faaboo mo gaanin Alla, o wonaano faabotoo…óo hoore-mun"
  28,82,"∆Åen yelinoo…ìe nokku makko on hanki mun, …ìe wa…óti wiide: \"Ee bone! Alla no wertana arsike on, Mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, O …ìi…ótinana [Mo O muuyani]. Si wanaa Alla mo∆¥∆¥inoo e amen, O mutinayno men. Ee bone! Jaka O malnataa yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  28,83,"∆äen galle laakara, Men wa…óanii …óe …ìen …ìe yi…óaa townitaare ka leydi, wanaa kadi bonnugol. Battane mo∆¥∆¥e …óen, ko fii gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  28,84,"Kala ardu…óo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, hino woodani mo ko …ìuri nde mo∆¥∆¥ude; kala kadi ardu…óo e bonannde, (yo o anndu) huuwu…ìe bon…ói …óin yo…ìetaake, si wanaa ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon"
  28,85,"Pellet, jippin…óo Alqur'aana on e maa…óa, ko ruttoo-wo ma ka woowaandi maa. Maaku: \"Ko Joomi am …ìuri anndude ardu…óo e peewal, e won…óo e majjere …ìanngunde"
  28,86,"A wonaano tam∆¥ininoo…óo jippineede Deftere nden e maa…óa. Si wanaa tun, ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa. Wata wonu muk, walloowo heefer…ìe …ìen"
  28,87,"wata …ìe falo ma kadi e Aayeeje Alla …óen, …ìaawo …óe jippineede e maa…óa. Noddu (yim…ìe …ìen) faade e Joomi maa, wata a wonu muk, jeyaa…óo e sirkoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,88,"Wata a rewudu e Alla, rewetee…óo goo. Rewetee…óo goo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Huunde fow re'ay, si wanaa Jaati Maako Kin. Ko Kanko woodani √±aawugol; ko ka Makko kadi ruttete…óon. @Corrected"
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  29,2,"E yim…ìe …ìen sikku …ìe accirte nii, fii …ìe wi'ii: \"Men gom…óinii!\" Hara …ìe fitninaaka"
  29,3,"Gom…óii, Men fitninii …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe. Maa Alla fe√±√±in, fii goongu…ìe …ìen, maa O fe√±√±in kadi, fii fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  29,4,"Kaa huuwu…ìe bon…ói …ìen sikku, wonnde …ìe laawoto Men? ko …ìe √±aawata kon bonii"
  29,5,"Kala taw…óo himo jortii hawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Anndu…óo On"
  29,6,"Kala kadi tii…ónii…óo, ko hoore-makko o tii…ónanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko yonndinii…óo e tageefo ngon"
  29,7,"∆Åen non gom…óim…ìe, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men momtan …ìe bon…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, Men yo…ìitra …ìe, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe gollaynoo kon"
  29,8,"Men yamirii ne…ó…óanke on, mo∆¥∆¥ugol e maw…ìe makko …ìen. Si …ìe doolii maa fii sirkangol Lam, ko a alanaa …óum ganndal, wata a …óofto …ìe ! Ko ka Am, woni ruttorde mon, Mi habra on, ko gollayno…óon"
  29,9,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Alla, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men wa…ótidu…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  29,10,"Hino e jim…ìe …ìen, wi'oowo: \"Men gom…óinii Alla\"; hara non si o tampiniraama fii Alla, o wa…óay lorra yim…ìe …ìen, wano lepte Alla …óen. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, pellet, …ìe wi'ay: \"Me…óen wondunoo e mo'on!\" Kere wanaa Alla …ìuri anndude ko woni e …ìer…óe tageefo ngon"
  29,11,"Ma Alla anndin fii gom…óim…ìe …ìen, ma O fe√±√±ina kadi fii naafiqii…ìe …ìen"
  29,12,"Heefer…ìe …ìen wi'ani gom…óim…ìe …ìen: \"Jokkee laawol amen ngol, men fawtoto fii goopi mon …óin\". Kono …ìe wonaali fawtotoo…ìe hay huunde e goopi ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, ko …ìe fenoo…ìe"
  29,13,"Kono maa …ìe fawtoo fii teddeendi junuubi ma…ì…ìe …óin, e teddeendi goo, wonndude e teddeendi ma…ì…ìe ndin. Ko maa …ìe lamndoyee, √ëalnde Darngal, gaay e kon ko …ìe fefindotonoo"
  29,14,"Gom…óii Men nulii Nuuhu e yim…ìe makko …ìen, o √±ii…ìi hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, duu…ìi ujunere, ≈ãakku…óum duu…ìi cappan…óe jowi. Waame on nanngi …ìe, hari ko …ìe too√±u…ìe"
  29,15,"Men da…óndi mo, kanko e yim…ìe laana kan; Men wa…ói ka kaawisa tageefo ngon"
  29,16,"(Janto) kadi Ibraahiima, nde o wi'annoo yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"Rewee Alla, hulon Mo; ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on, si woni hi…óon anndi"
  29,17,"Anndee ko reweton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, hi…óon ta∆¥a fenaande. Pellet, …óin …ói rewoton gaanin Alla, …ói waawaa on arsikude; …óa…ì…ìiree arsike on ka Alla, rewon Mo, yetton Mo. Ko ka Makko woni ruttete…óon"
  29,18,"Si on fennii, haray mofte adinoo…ìe kadi fenniino (Nulaa…ìe mun). Alaa ko fawii e Nulaa…óo on, si wanaa yottingol …ìannginngol"
  29,19,"E …ìee yi'aali no Alla fu…ó…óorta tagu ngun, refti O ruttay ngu? Pellet, …óum wonii ko newanii Alla"
  29,20,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron no O fu…ó…óori tagu ngun. Refti Alla taga tagu sakkitoru ngun. Pellet, Alla ko hattan…óo kala huunde"
  29,21,"Himo lepte mo O muuyani, O yurmo mo O muuyani; ko ka Makko ruttete…óon"
  29,22,"On wonaali laawotoo…ìe ka leydi, wanaa ka kammu; alanaa on gaanin Alla, woni gi…óo, wanaa ballo"
  29,23,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Alla …óen, e hawroygol e Makko ngol, …ìen ta∆¥ike e yurmeende Am, …ìen …óon, hino woodani …ìe lepte muusu…óe"
  29,24,"Jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano, si wanaa wiide …ìe: \"Waree mo, maa sunnon mo\". Kono Alla da…óndi mo e yiite ngen. Pellet, wonii e …óum, maandeeji, wonannde yim…ìe gom…óim…ìe"
  29,25,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, fii yi…óindiro hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna, hooti non, √ëalnde Darndal, yoga mon yeddoyay yoga, yoga mon kadi hu…óo yoga, hara non, jaa∆¥orde mon nden, ko ka Yiite, hara walloo…ìe alanaa on"
  29,26,"Luutu gom…óini mo. O maaki: \"Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  29,27,"Men ye…ói mo Ismaa'iila e Yaaquuba, Men wa…ói e geyngol makko ngol, Annabaaku e Daftere. Men okki mo mbarjaari makko ndin aduna, pellet, kanko on ka laakara, ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  29,28,"(Janto) kadi luutu, nde o maakannoo yim…ìe makko …ìen : \" E on aray e pankare, …óe gooto e winndere nden adaaki on e mun"
  29,29,"E on aray yottagol e wor…ìe …ìen? palo…óon kadi e laawol? Huuwon ko mbatirdu mon ko a√±inii?\" Kono jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano, si wanaa wiide …ìe: \"Addan men lepte Alla …óen, si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  29,30,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, wallam e hoore yim…ìe bonnoo…ìe …ìen"
  29,31,"Tuma nde Imminaa…ìe Amen …ìen addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, …ìe wi\"i: \"Menen, ko men halkoo…ìee yim…ìe ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yim…ìe mayre laatike too√±oo…ìe"
  29,32,"O maaki: \"Kono Luutu no ton!\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko menen …ìuri anndude fii won…ìe ton. Ko ma men da…óndu mo, kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen, si wanaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketee…ìe …ìen"
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaa…ìe Amen …ìen hewtunoo ka Luutu, o sa…ótiraa fii ma…ì…ìe, …ìernde makko …ìi…ótorii fii ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu, wata a suno. Ko men da…óndoo…ìe ma an e …ìeynguure maa nden, si wanaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaa…ìe …ìen"
  29,34,"Ko men jippinoo…ìe lepte e yim…ìe ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko …ìe yaltunoo e …óoftaare kon"
  29,35,"Gom…óii Men accii e nden (saare), maande …ìanngunde, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe …ìen"
  29,36,"(Men nuli) kadi e Madyana, musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, rewee Alla, jortoron √ëalannde sakkitiinde nden, wata woniri e leydi ndin, bonnoo…ìe"
  29,37,"Kono …ìe fenni mo. Dillannde nden nanngi …ìe, …ìe wa…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìe jiccii…ìe-maayi"
  29,38,"(Men halki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. Gom…óii caambbeje ma…ì…ìe …óin …ìannganii on. Seytaane cu…óinani …ìe, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen, ndu sakkii …ìe e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko …ìe rentunoo…ìe"
  29,39,"(Men halki) kadi Qaaruuna, e Fir'awna e Haamaana. Gom…óii le, Muusaa addanii …ìe …ìanngannduyeeji, kono …ìe townitii ka leydi, …ìe wonaano laawotoo…ìe"
  29,40,"Kala ma…ì…ìe, Men leptirno junuubi mun …óin: no e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men wuurti henndu e mun; no e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe haacaango halki; no e ma…ì…ìe, mo Men mutini …óum ka leydi, no e ma…ì…ìe kadi, …ìe Men yoolunoo. Kono non, Alla siforaali too√±oowo …ìe; si ko woni, ko kam…ìe too√±unoo ko'e ma…ì…ìe"
  29,41,"Misal …ìen jogitii…ìe gaanin Alla rewetee…ói, ko wano marijaawowal(njomblo) saccungal suudu. Ko …ìuri lo'ude non e cuu…ói …óin, ko suudu marijaawo. Sinno …ìe annduno"
  29,42,"Pellet, Alla no anndi kala huunde nde …ìe noddata gaanin Makko. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  29,43,"∆äee ko mise …óe Men piyanta yim…ìe …ìen; ko woni tun, faamataa …óen, si wanaa anndu…ìe …ìen"
  29,44,"Alla tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e hoore goonga. Pellet, wonii …óum, maande, wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  29,45,"Janngu kon ko waayinaa e maa…óa ka Deftere, √±ii…ìaa e julde nden. Pellet, juulde nden no ha…óa pankare e ko a√±inii. Ko jantagol Alla ngol …ìuri (huunde kala) mawnude. Alla no anndi ko golloton kon"